HEADWORD: pacifist
<hw>pacifist</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A person opposed to
violence as a means of settling disputes.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pacificist, disarmer.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A person whose strong belief in pacifism causes
him/her to refuse to participate in military activities, especially one
who refuses to be drafted into the armed forces.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pacifistic</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>pacifist</ent>⟦br⟧
